  "_doc": "Short name -> Hinge-friendly search string. The first autocomplete suggestion for these strings should be the city itself, not a landmark/airport. Add your own; test with `python -c 'import locations; locations.set_location(\"name\")'`. Copy this file to locations.json before editing.",
